<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">أما الستة الأولى فنحو:</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> <span class="c1">"كاذب"</span> مِن: كَذِب.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> <span class="c1">"نَصَر"</span> مِن: نَصْر.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> <span class="c1">"ضارِب"</span> مِن: ضَرْب.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c4">[٤]</span> <span class="c1">"ذَهَبَ"</span> مِن: ذَهَاب.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c4">[٥]</span> <span class="c1">"سَفْر"</span> جمع سافر اسم فاعل مِن: سَفَر.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span><span class="c4">[٦]</span> <span class="c1">"سِرْ"</span> مِن: سَيْر، لكن مع اعتبار حركة الإعراب، وقد يُمثل بِـ <span class="c1">"صَبٍّ"</span> اسم فاعل <span class="c1">"الصبابة"</span>.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span><span class="c5">وأما الأربعة التي بعدها فنحو:</span><a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span><span class="c4">[٧]</span> <span class="c1">"مُدَحْرَج"</span> <span class="c4">[اسم مفعول]</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span> مِن: دَحْرَجَة.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
